  "1137750": {
    "name": "Farmer's Life",
    "steam_appid": 1137750,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌾“农民的生活”-释放内心的农民！ 🚜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在“农夫的生活”中深入体验乡村生活的质朴魅力，在这里您将在充满活力的农场体验生活的乐趣和挑战。 种植、发展和拥抱一个生活在广阔开放世界中的国家。 您做主、创造并从不同的机制和无限的可能性中进行选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/130d5f83c8a33ed5ec3d0e846ac0ff00.poster.avif?t=1772060338\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/130d5f83c8a33ed5ec3d0e846ac0ff00.webm?t=1772060338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐷 照顾各种动物：你的责任包括鸡、猪、山羊、绵羊、牛，甚至是雄伟的马。 培养他们，他们将为您提供宝贵的资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/4123f3afe07089602d7e3ed31049c959.poster.avif?t=1772060338\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/4123f3afe07089602d7e3ed31049c959.webm?t=1772060338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌾 农场生活等待着您：卷起袖子，亲力亲为，耕耘、种植和收获农作物，以维持您的农场和生计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/07fbb5b5528f9c3554574a158286ae82.poster.avif?t=1772060338\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/07fbb5b5528f9c3554574a158286ae82.webm?t=1772060338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛠️ 建造你的梦想农场：建造一切，从舒适的房子到坚固的栅栏、大门、棚屋等等。 按照您的愿望塑造您的农场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/c72fccb52fd19b209161430248914e32.poster.avif?t=1772060338\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/c72fccb52fd19b209161430248914e32.webm?t=1772060338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍲 烹饪冒险等待着您：探索烹饪艺术，使用农场的食材准备各种美味又实用的餐点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏹 狩猎刺激：接受狩猎狐狸、野猪、鹿甚至熊的挑战。 将您成功的狩猎变成战利品和毛皮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪓 收集大自然的恩赐：冒险进入野外，从蜂箱中收集木材、覆盆子、蓝莓、蘑菇、鸡蛋和蜂蜜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/ba016f94979be4f51fd2ed2c8fe4aa46.poster.avif?t=1772060338\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/ba016f94979be4f51fd2ed2c8fe4aa46.webm?t=1772060338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍾 制作、购买、销售和饮用酒精：酿造和销售自己的酒精饮料，成为酿酒厂的大师。 别忘了享受你的劳动成果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👰 寻找爱情和陪伴：通过婚礼和支持您的配偶来分享您的旅程，体验婚姻生活的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💰 贸易繁荣：参与熙熙攘攘的贸易市场，您可以在这里买卖物品来积累财富并扩大农场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💬 史诗般的任务等待着：踏上众多任务，让你连续几个小时投入其中，挑战你的技能和决策能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/b1f5c8426a2c1c87391ecceff1ace9c0.poster.avif?t=1772060338\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/b1f5c8426a2c1c87391ecceff1ace9c0.webm?t=1772060338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐎 选择您的座驾：以时尚的方式游览您的农场。 无论您喜欢自行车、马车、拖拉机还是摩托车，您都有选择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌎 无限自由：享受沙盒体验，您可以自由决定自己想做什么以及如何经营农场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌱 动态季节：适应不断变化的季节，作物选择和策略全年都很重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/d723c118fb9eac4c23e1ed211a0f3864.poster.avif?t=1772060338\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/d723c118fb9eac4c23e1ed211a0f3864.webm?t=1772060338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚜 掌握独特的机器：控制各种独特的农业机械，从割草机到犁、播种机、挖掘机、撒布机等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/3df650b4a04d65623729faeafcb64dde.poster.avif?t=1772060338\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137750/extras/3df650b4a04d65623729faeafcb64dde.webm?t=1772060338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💣 一点混乱：通过骑猪和造成无害的混乱等有趣的活动来发泄一下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺️ 探索丰富的世界：探索掩体、废墟房屋、古老教堂、雷区、池塘和蜿蜒的河流，发掘隐藏的宝藏和秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《农民的生活》不仅仅是一款游戏，更是一款游戏。 这是一场引人入胜的农场冒险，你的选择将塑造你的命运。 发现乡村生活的乐趣，让自己沉浸在无限可能的世界中。 你能从头开始建立你的农场帝国吗？</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 波兰语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 韩语, 俄语, 简体中文, 土耳其语, 捷克语, 匈牙利语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
